{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act9d0_level_act9d0_04_beg","storyGroup":"act9d0","storySort":7,"storyDependence":"act9d0_level_act9d0_03_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"DM-6","storyName":"远遁","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"一夜之间，战争倾斜。得知情报的赫德雷被迫重回战场，找到了疯狂复仇中的W。赫德雷邀请W回到队伍，而他们将前往乌萨斯的冻土。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act9d0/level_act9d0_04_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act9d0_06","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":5,"next":7,"characters":["赫德雷","伊内丝","W","萨卡兹战士","？？？"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Character","id":4},{"type":"Blocker","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":5},{"type":"Dialog","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"Text","text":"我自己明明说过，谁也不能置身事外。","id":7},{"type":"Text","text":"结果我自己还是想要逃离这场战争，因此从巴别塔，从W和殿下那里......","id":8},{"type":"Text","text":"逃走了。","id":9},{"type":"Text","text":"......真是矛盾。","id":10},{"type":"Text","text":"后悔吗？也许吧。","id":11},{"type":"Text","text":"但我就算在那里，也做不成任何事情。","id":12},{"type":"Dialog","id":13},{"type":"Character","id":14},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":15},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_barracks","screenadapt":"coverall","id":16},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":17},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$mist_intro","key":"$mist_loop","volume":"0.4","id":18,"musicid":0},{"type":"Text","text":"5:58  A.M.    天气/小雨","id":19},{"type":"Text","text":"卡兹戴尔最北部边郊，战区边缘，佣兵营地","id":20},{"type":"Text","text":"离开巴别塔数月后","id":21},{"type":"dialog","id":22},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_047","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":23},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"这份情报......","id":25,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......","id":26,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":27},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......","id":28,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"说点什么吧，你比较擅长这个，能说会道。","id":29,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":30},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......说点什么呢。","id":31,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"干嘛把问题抛回来......？","id":33,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......僵持了这么久的战局，会在一夜之间倾斜吗？","id":34,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"这半年多发生了什么？这太快了......","id":35,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":36},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"我们都知道有哪里出了问题。","id":37,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"但是，是哪里。没人知道。","id":38,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"不，应该说是不敢知道。","id":39,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"殿下......还有殿下身边的那些人，他们不该沦落到如此下场，我们都这么觉得。","id":40,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":41},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"但是现在......我们的下场呢？也会是这样吗？","id":42,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":43},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"太早了。这场战争结束的太早了。","id":44,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"直到上个月我们都还在履行和巴别塔的战略合约，联络突然中断，了无音讯......","id":45,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"所有人都知道我们是哪一边的，我们甚至还没准备好离开这里。","id":46,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......如果真的就这么戛然而止，我们只会无处可逃。","id":47,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"让信使再去联系一趟在各地的线人，打听所有能打听到的情报。","id":48,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"也许我们必须......回到战场正中了。","id":49,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":50},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"虽然，我也预料到会有这么一天。","id":51,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"我们其实都知道的，不是吗？","id":52,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"如果我们真的想彻底撒手不管，当时就没必要答应他们的请求。","id":53,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"靠我们自己逃离这里，翻过瓦兰登湖，在其他地方继续大展拳脚——","id":54,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":55},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"伊内丝，我——","id":56,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":57},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"打住。","id":58,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"我们很难从那里脱身，那份温暖太容易令人茫然，我们都沉醉于此。","id":59,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":60},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"也许我们就应该彻底抛下巴别塔，带着我们的人离开。","id":61,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":62},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"还是老毛病，你又变得多愁善感起来了。","id":63,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":64},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"从什么时候开始，我似乎没有做过任何一个有利于我们的决定。","id":65,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"也许我们已经不该继续待在战场上......","id":66,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"够了，你是萨卡兹还是我是萨卡兹？","id":68,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"这片大地还有任何其他哪怕一处避雨的木棚，容纳得下我们这些手染鲜血的萨卡兹吗？","id":69,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"别总是这么自责，责任是我们共同承担的。","id":70,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"还有，就目前来看，那时候你选择接纳W，还算是个不错的决定。","id":71,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"她帮我们挣了不少钱，也干掉了不少人。","id":72,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......但愿吧。","id":74,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"W......她还活着吗？","id":75,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":76},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"我觉得她没那么容易死掉。","id":77,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":78},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"她在殿下身边的时日也不短了，说不定她会知道更多的事情。","id":79,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"我们必须迅速把握住现在卡兹戴尔的一切导向，如果能重新找到她，也许事情会变得简单一点。","id":80,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"我们真的要依靠她作为后盾？","id":82,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......","id":84,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"好吧。","id":86,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":87},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......真遗憾。","id":88,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":89},{"type":"Dialog","id":90},{"type":"Character","id":91},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":92},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_battlefield","screenadapt":"coverall","id":93},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":94},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":95},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":96},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":97},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"——找到了，哎，你还真是能跑啊。","id":98,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"$nervous_loop","crossfade":"2","volume":"0.4","id":99,"musicid":1},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":100},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"你看上去心如死灰，我听说过你最近在做什么，W。","id":101,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"1","id":102},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"那你也应该知道，你是最后一个了。","id":103,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":104},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"没错，你都看见了，这场仗死了很多人。","id":105,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"你只是在近乎麻木地增加这个数字。","id":106,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"即使是从我的立场而言，还没死掉的任何一个人做的事情，都比你的所作所为更有意义。","id":107,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"1","id":108},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"闭嘴。","id":109,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":110},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"要我提醒你一遍吗？","id":111,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"特蕾西娅已经死了。整个卡兹戴尔，整个泰拉大陆都会知道卡兹戴尔的新王当立。","id":112,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"那只是一次斩首行动，你们依旧保留了很多核心成员。","id":113,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"比如那个指挥官再也没有出现过，他们做出了正确的选择。","id":114,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"殿下没有彻底赶尽杀绝，是因为他希望尽快终结混乱的局面，卡兹戴尔需要殿下开辟下一段道路——","id":115,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"——至于你呢？你是来谈论对错的吗？","id":116,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"你当然不会发问，但你心里就是这么想的，一边这么想，一边把当时出现在你视野里的面孔一个一个抹杀掉。","id":117,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"说到底你只是来宣泄个人情绪的，小佣兵，沉浸在自己不值一提的复仇里。","id":118,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"你赢不了任何人。","id":119,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"1","id":120},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"反正我赢得过你，而且会很轻松。","id":121,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":122},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"杀得掉我，不能说明什么。","id":123,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"1","id":124},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"你的话很多哎，到底是在猜我的心思，还是单纯在死之前，发泄你自己的想法？","id":125,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":126},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"都有，我没必要否认。","id":127,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"自从那个凯——自从我差点被同伴喷出的鲜血所窒息之后，我就握不住武器了。","id":128,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"我们都流了血，洒满巴别塔的殿堂，你眼里的景象，在我眼里只会更加真切。","id":129,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"既然你找到了我，那我必死无疑，呵。","id":130,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"我知道。","id":131,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"dialog","id":132},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","id":133},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":134},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":135},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$pistol","id":136},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":137},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":138},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","id":139},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"别扯那么多，对于杀你这件事......我只是想这么做而已，就当是排解一下失业的压力吧。","id":140,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_053","id":141},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"呸......我真是低估你了，疯子。","id":142,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"你真能像这样一点愤怒都没有地扣下扳机？还是说，你真的疯到了连自己的情绪都感觉不到？","id":143,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"你只身一人......还想继续这样追杀多少同胞？","id":144,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"你以为......你的这种举动不是在为特雷西斯殿下考虑？你帮他灭口，你还......","id":145,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"1","id":146},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"不要喋喋不休了，想死的难道不是你吗？","id":147,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"如果你逃回你亲爱的摄政王身边，我还当真能杀穿卡兹戴尔，把你们一个个揪出来不成？","id":148,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"你没有。你们都没有。杀了她的你们，不可能再回到卡兹戴尔，再回到你们过去的样子。","id":149,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"除了那些真正的怪物，没人还能在看见她的表情后无动于衷。","id":150,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"所以你们一直等着一个人，等着我这个刽子手，我只是来解脱你而已。","id":151,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"不收钱就已经很客气了，知足吧。","id":152,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":153},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"......","id":154,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"嘁......自以为是的疯子......","id":155,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"但你说的也没错......","id":156,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"我们......我们亲手染上了她的血......她在最后甚至......","id":157,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"我......","id":158,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"dialog","id":159},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","id":160},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":161},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.9","id":162},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":163},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":164},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":165},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"你就不该称那个人为“殿下”，殿下只有特蕾西娅。不然你还可以多说几句。","id":166,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"篡位者最好不要急着给自己加冕，反正都要掉脑袋的，那样浪费王冠，等到特蕾西娅......","id":167,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"嘁。","id":168,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"特蕾西娅......","id":169,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","id":170},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"拒降者会被其他佣兵追猎的，下一次，你就是猎物了。","id":171},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","id":172},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"——是你们。","id":173,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"我以为你们早就离开卡兹戴尔境内了......很久不见。","id":174,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"dialog","id":175},{"type":"Character","id":176},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":177},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":179},{"type":"dialog","id":180},{"type":"Character","id":181},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":182},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_047","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":183},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":184},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......比起这场漫长的战争，我们也没有太长时间不见，你的成长速度还真是惊人。","id":185,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","id":186},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"好像是呢，你的手在抖喔。","id":187,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":188},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"我只是有些生疏。","id":189,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_046#2","focus":"1","id":190},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"虽然有情报指出你在这附近独自活动——","id":191,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"但这里离塔巴镇都有将近两百公里，你拖着摇摇晃晃的身体想去哪里？","id":192,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"不，还是说你从那之后就这么一边独自行动一边转移，持续了数个月——？","id":193,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_046#2","focus":"2","id":194},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"也没有很辛苦，就是一个人做很多事情不太方便。","id":195,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_046#2","focus":"1","id":196},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"比如，你现在一身草草处理的伤势，随时有感染加剧的风险？","id":197,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_046#2","focus":"2","id":198},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"没死掉就行，我可没那么容易倒下。","id":199,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"倒是那座塔楼......有点眼熟，这是哪里？","id":200,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":201},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"这里？西部战区边缘，坐标——","id":202,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"——啊啊，这里是“W”死的地方。","id":203,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"也是你加入我们的地方。","id":204,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","id":205},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":".......这里已经完全变成废墟了。","id":206,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"怎么？想故地重游？","id":207,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","id":208},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"我像是那么有情调的人吗？只是最后一个目标逃到这里来而已。","id":209,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"我知道你们来找我做什么，像上次一样，咱们直接开门见山吧。","id":210,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":211},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......摄政王已经统合了卡兹戴尔的所有武装力量。","id":212,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"残存的雇佣兵也会被团结起来，组成一支真正的军队，然后被遣往大地各处。","id":213,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":214},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"真是着急呢。","id":215,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":216},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"可以理解。","id":217,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"除非维多利亚和拉特兰的权贵都是些脑子装满黄油的废物，否则没人会坐视卡兹戴尔在统一后还有喘息的空间。","id":218,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":219},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"那也许我们可以借某些人的手再次挑起内乱。","id":220,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":221},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"就算你想复仇，这也不是个好选择。","id":222,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":223},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"别忘了，现在跟着我们的人有不少都曾和特蕾西娅并肩作战。","id":224,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_046#2","focus":"1","id":225},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"萨卡兹雇佣兵从来都没有明确立场。大部分人已经对思考感到麻木，他们只需要一个方向。","id":226,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"所以全体萨卡兹都会听命于摄政王，他已经赢了。","id":227,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_046#2","focus":"2","id":228},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"——伊内丝，你把你的角打磨成萨卡兹的形状那时候，疼吗？会流血吗？","id":229,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_046#2","focus":"1","id":230},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......不会。","id":231,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_046#2","focus":"2","id":232},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"那你的这份面目就根本没有钉入血肉，太肤浅了，继续装作一个萨卡兹，你会死的。","id":233,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_046#2","focus":"1","id":234},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"谢谢你扭曲到让人咂舌的好意。","id":235,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_046#2","focus":"2","id":236},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"我只是不想在这个时候，还听见你自诩“萨卡兹”。","id":237,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_046#2","focus":"1","id":238},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"但我决定要继续这样走下去，我只能这样走下去。","id":239,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":240},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"W，自特蕾西娅殿下失踪后，卡兹戴尔就已经变了，天翻地覆。","id":241,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"大多萨卡兹别无选择，更何况对很多人而言，这个选择充满诱惑。","id":242,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":243},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"......所以，没来得及彻底脱身的你们，也接受了这个那个凶手的提议？","id":244,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":245},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"否则我们只会是冰凉的尸体。","id":246,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":247},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"看来，我是说服不了你们放弃了。","id":248,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"我可不会像赫德雷当时那么坏心眼，既然都是老相识了......就直接动手吧。","id":249,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":250},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"别总是这么着急......也许你会对接下来的事情感兴趣。","id":251,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......我们不会回到卡兹戴尔，我们会去乌萨斯。","id":252,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":253},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"——这可是个意料之外的答案，早点说啊，我差点就动手了。","id":254,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"这下有点意思了不是吗，说说看呗，赫德雷队长。","id":255,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"dialog","id":256},{"type":"Dialog","id":257},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":258},{"type":"image","id":259},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_ac9_2","x":"30","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"0","id":260},{"type":"ImageTween","xFrom":"30","xTo":"-50","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","duration":"25","block":"false","text":"","id":261},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":262},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"在卡兹戴尔之外的大地上，有一些......感染者势力正在崛起。","id":263,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"他们向雇佣兵提出了丰厚的价格，同时摄政王也希望能借此操纵一部分感染者为他的计划所用......","id":264,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"......感染者势力？","id":265,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"但他们的核心力量，目前尚且停留在乌萨斯的冻土之上。","id":266,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"而摄政王的视野也早就离开了这座破败的卡兹戴尔，王位空置，他早已身在别处。","id":267,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"聚集了各个种族被压迫、被歧视者的整合运动，正适合摆放在下一个被需要的位置上。","id":268,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":269},{"type":"Character","id":270},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":271},{"type":"image","id":272},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":273},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"所以加入那个什么整合运动而远离卡兹戴尔，不会有人因此起疑。","id":275,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"然后呢？","id":276,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":277},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......然后走一步看一步，W。","id":278,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"你知道我想要的是什么，我也许也知道你想要什么。","id":279,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":280},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"......","id":281,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"你说得对，这似乎可行性更高。","id":282,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"嗯，毕竟我要找的那个人，可是个真正的怪物啊。","id":283,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"而且那个老女人也消失了......继续待在卡兹戴尔的确不妥......","id":284,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"......但这一次就不是你们两个说了算了，我有想做的事情，我要自己决定，没问题吧？","id":285,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":286},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"摄政王会派人来统合这一批佣兵军队的，如果只是说我们的小队之间......可以。","id":287,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"我们会帮你的。","id":288,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":289},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"没关系，我一向很擅长“应付”上司。","id":290,"figure":"avg_npc_046#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_046#2","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":291},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......那很好。","id":292,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"欢迎归队，“W”。","id":293,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":294},{"type":"Image","id":295},{"type":"Character","id":296},{"type":"dialog","id":297},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":298},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":299},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_ac9_6","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"0","id":300},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"false","id":301},{"type":"ImageTween","xScaleFrom":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"25","block":"false","id":302},{"type":"Text","text":"......远离卡兹戴尔。","id":303},{"type":"Text","text":"W变了很多，她应该有她自己的想法。","id":304},{"type":"Text","text":"伊内丝被我推上了这条路，但她比想象中坚强。","id":305},{"type":"Text","text":"......我呢？","id":306},{"type":"Text","text":"偶尔可以从一些险峻的地势眺望到烟雾笼罩中的卡兹戴尔。","id":307},{"type":"Text","text":"卡兹戴尔。","id":308},{"type":"Text","text":"我也许，才是那个最想逃离卡兹戴尔的人。","id":309},{"type":"dialog","id":310},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":311},{"type":"Dialog","id":312},{"type":"Blocker","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":313}],"characters":["赫德雷","伊内丝","W","萨卡兹战士","？？？"]}